Cricket Start is a Chrome Extension for the New Tab
Introducing the Cricket Start Chrome Extension for your New Tab: Dive into the World of Cricket!

Brought to you by Virtue Traffic Ltd.

Get direct access to top-tier Cricket sites for up-to-the-minute scores, the latest news, and more. We bring you an unparalleled sports experience right on your new tab. Get fast and easy access to major websites with Cricket news and updates.
The search features within this extension are driven by Microsoft Bing.

By adding the "Cricket Start" extension to your browser, you're accepting its Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.

While the search capabilities in the extension come from Microsoft Bing, rest assured it won't modify any settings associated with your primary browser search.
